title: #196 - Shane Dawson, Dr Disrespect, Tati Westbrook, Chris D'Elia
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast the gang recap one of the most dramatic couple of weeks ever in the creator sphere- from Shane Dawson's rapid fall from grace, Tati Westbrook shiving him while he was already down, Dr Disrespect being disappeared by agents of the NWO, Chris D'Elia being exposed as a sex fiend, and a whole lot more!
